11. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating pepper##1
12. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
13. the person eating corn is the person who's sport is rowing##1
14. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
15. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person eating pear and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |  7   |
| Sport   | sailing | weightlifting      | rowing | volleyball     | badminton     | soccer   | golf |
| Food       | mango    | cucumber | corn    | raspberry | pepper     | strawberry | pear |
| Pet        | snake    | goldfish | goat    | rabbit    | guinea-pig | chinchilla | bird |

